title: A Redtail's Dream - Complete Run, 2011-2013 {WebComixFan}
description:
"A REDTAIL'S DREAM" Web Comic

"A Redtail's Dream" (minnasundberg.fi/artd.php) by Minna Sundberg is a tale steeped in Finnish lore, revolving around the tribulations of a human boy named Hannu and his shapeshifting dog, Ville, as they embark on a reluctant journey through the realm of dreams to correct a cosmic mishap on the part of the young spirit, Puppy Fox.

This torrent collects the entire run of the series, from 2011 through 2013, in a series of CBR files, one for each chapter. These are not scans of published volumes; all comics were downloaded from the Web site
